'''DuroDelve Industries''' was a [[Duros/Legends|Duros]] mining company. They bought the rights to the majority of [[Glydus Mining Corporation]]'s equipment and facilities after that company went bankrupt before the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]]. DuroDelve was later nationalized by the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]], and they lost control over most of their property, with the exception of the [[Glydus Mining Platform]].<ref name="University">{{GamerCite|2|The University of Sanbra Guide to Intelligent Life: The Duros}}</ref>

